name: Dandelion Seed Necklace - Gold Dandelion Necklace - Dandelion Necklace
description:
This Gold Wish Necklace is a 10 mm Glass ball filled with Dandelion Seeds and covered with a gold plated leaf cap on the bottom and a Gold Plated Bead cap on top completed with a tiny gold plated ball and hanging from Gold Filled Chain. The jump rings and spring ring clasp are also gold filled.

It’s 16” long and can be adjusted to your preferred length up to 20 inches. Anything longer there will be an additional charge. 

Please allow 5 to 7 business days from date of payment received for your items to ship. I try to create each piece as they are ordered to allow for customizations of the items. 

If you would like a piece in a different length or ear wire please contact me as my customer's satisfaction is my top priority. 

All items ship using the USPS Mail Service with Delivery Confirmation. I will send you a tracking number as soon as your package ships. If you would like to upgrade your shipping to Priority Mail, please let me know and I will adjust your listing to show the shipping difference.
